tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE CustomerFeedback (
  feedback_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  feedback_text TEXT NOT NULL,
  customer_id INT NOT NULL,
  customer_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  feedback_date DATE,
  market_trend VARCHAR(100)
)

CREATE TABLE customer_feedback_analysis (
  analysis_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  feedback_id INT,
  trend_id INT,
  feedback_rating INT,
  analysis_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE FeedbackAnalysis (
  analysis_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  feedback_id INT,
  trend_id INT,
  innovation_id INT,
  sector_id INT,
  analysis_date DATE
);
